Title: Redefining South Africa's economic trajectory
Author-Name: BER team
Abstract: With the appropriate policy choices, South Africa does not need miracles or fairy tales for a better outcome. We need sustained implementation of existing structural reform plans. Taking Operation Vulindlela (OV) as a starting point, this note explores what would be needed to lift South Africa’s trajectory to a faster, stronger growth path. 
